  <acronym>PERFUSE</acronym>
  <official_title>Expanding the Time Window for IV Thrombolysis With Rt-PA in Acute Ischemic Stroke Patients Using Computed Tomography Perfusion Imaging: The PERFusion Use in Stroke Evaluation (PERFUSE) Study</official_title>
